  "content": {
    "visible_text": "Kids Class Schedule Kids classes are open to all experience levels. Beginners and new students are always welcome, and your first week of classes is free! Please let us know you are coming by scheduling an orientation and trial class using this quick form . Class Schedule : Monday:       4:30-5:30pm Tuesday:       4:15–5:15pm Wednesday: 5:15-6:00pm Thursday:     4:15–5:15pm Friday:           5:00–5:30pm (Kids Red Belt) Friday:           5:30–6:30pm Saturday:    10:00–11:00am Please note that enrolled students are required to attend at least two classes per week (excluding vacations). For our latest up-to-date schedule, please consult and subscribe to our Google Calendar: Reviews Facebook Community Dojo Quantum Martial Arts is a registered 501(c)(3) nonprofit in the State of California, and we thrive on the generosity of people like you. All donations are tax-deductible. Quantum’s tax ID number is 26-1534597. No donation is too small, or too large. Whether it’s $20 or $20,000, every cent will be hugely appreciated and put to good use. Support Our Kids Donate now to support our youth scholarship program which allows families in need to train at reduced cost. We believe investment in our community involves investing in our youth. Our Sister Schools Our Seattle Dojo has served thousands of students since opening on Capitol Hill in 1995, and currently offers youth and adult classes in the Central District. Our Portland Dojo was established in 2020, and currently offers youth and adult classes in Southeast Portland. A WordPress.com Website .",
